body:
Detective Pikachu Spoiler Free Review

OK first, Pikachu is freaking adorable. The animation is such a wonderful satisfaction. This film was honestly very enjoyable. It pays some wonderful homage to long and short term pokemon fans alike. The first couple of kf scenes in particular are what catch your attention to detail. Found myself naming out all the pokemon as I can see. Pika Reynolds does the role to an exceptional standard in true Reynolds fashion. I honestly believe simply being a Pokemon fan will make you enjoy this movie. If Pokemon GO was a permanent VR experience for the world, this would be it. I feel the story will put off some people but overall I personally enjoyed it and I am sure many others will to. Its definitely worth a watch.

Final Note : Thank God I have VIP access to one of the only high tier cinemas in Remnant. Perks of being a Schnee I guess.

summary: Ash: (as he's going to battle with Kirby) Alright, Charizard! Let's do this thing! (Releases Charizard) Okay, so Kirby is a...
body:
Ash: (as he’s going to battle with Kirby) Alright, Charizard! Let’s do this thing! (Releases Charizard) Okay, so Kirby is a tricky opponent, so we gotta- (turns to find Charizard gone) Huh? Where did you go? (Sees Charizard running away)

Charizard: (panicking) No more wet willies!!!!

Ash: …Kirby?

Kirby: What? You said once he wouldn’t listen to you, so I trained him myself!

Ash: (unamused) Kirby…

Kirby: Besides, I wasn’t really going to give him a wet willy. It’s called scare tactics, Ash!

title: Lairon - 305
body:

summary: SK JAPAN RELEASING POKEMON AND KIRBY CANDY-THEMED VINYL POUCHES
title: SK JAPAN RELEASING POKEMON AND KIRBY CANDY-THEMED VINYL POUCHES
body: This might look like a new Pokemon candy for Japan, but that’s not actually the case. SK Japan is releasing a series of vinyl storage bags for various items, and while the outside of the bags might look like candy packaging, there’s no actual candy inside. The lineup includes Pokemon and Kirby pouches, and will release sometime in June 2019.
